Golden milk

Ingredients:
1. 300 ml. milk (you can use any kind of milk you want)
2. 1 tsp. kurkuma
3. 1/2 tsp. cayennepepper
4. 1/2 tsp. cinnamon
5. a pinch of black pepper
6. 1/2 of peeled ginger root or 1/4 tsp. ginger powder
7. 1 tbs. honey

Instructions:
1. First, blend all the ingredients in a high speed blender until smooth.
2. Then, poor into small sauce pan and heat 3-5 minutes over medium heat until hot but not boiling
3. Drink immediately.
